<h3 id='slide_when_moving'>: slide_when_moving()</h3><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight lua tab-lua"><code><span class="kd">local</span>   <span class="p">;</span><span class="c1">-- example </span>
<span class="p">:</span><span class="n">slide_when_moving</span><span class="p">(</span> <span class="kc">true</span> <span class="p">)</span>
</code></pre></div>
<p>If <code>true</code>, this  will slide to another  when it moves, instead of teleporting.</p>
<h4 id='function-call'>Function Call</h4>
<p><code>:slide_when_moving( should_slide )</code></p>
<h4 id='parameters'>Parameters</h4>
<p><code>should_slide</code><br>
    &emsp;If <code>true</code>, this  will slide between s when moving. Otherwise, it teleports.</p>
